reviewText:
I  already loved the album when it first came out, so I knew the dvd would be just as good. There's nice extensions to the songs.
Only reason why I gave 4 and not 5 was because she didn't perform Solid Rock on the dvd.

To God be the Glory for TASHA COBBS !!!!! This DVD is amazing !! It felt like I was actually there ! The room was filled with 3,000 worshippers !!! And it was beyond POWERFUL ! You hear the MATURITY in her worship and voice my GOD ! This DVD is a must have for worshippers all over the world !
Great DVD you get to worship with her through the whole concert!!
Fantastic! Beware that the Jamie Grace song (as heard on the playlist) is not included. I was disappointed. Overall, fantastic praise and worship!

OMG! The DVD is amazing...if you already have the album or not, the DVD is definitely well worth getting as well to complete your collection. You will be blessed and anointed by sister Tasha Cobbs. I can't stop singing He Still Love Me. You will be Putting A Praise all over your living room. Get to know Tasha Cobbs... Get it, get It and get it. I see you do the Baptist fit.... Love her. Tasha Cobbs is a Blessing.
This DVD exceeded my expectations.
This is an excellent at home worship experience!
Love this DVD.
I love her album so i knew I'd love her dvd
One of my favorite singer she gets down.
This artist never disappoints. Lyrics amazing. Perfect for praise & worshipl
Amazing DVD!!!

Tasha Cobbs has a real gift and obvious annointing. It was great watching her and her team "live." It wasn't a performance because their hearts were in worship. Well done.

Amazing worship! Playing the cd just brought the Holy Ghost into the room and had me all in tears! Tasha Cobbs is God's blessing upon all worshippers. May her anointing be increased manifold.

Tasha Cobbs was AMAZING IN THE video. I love her music and she clearly has an anointing on her life. My only complaint is the resolution on the video is not that great. I am a little disappointed with the video quality.
